title.native: モンスター娘のお医者さん

description:
Here in the town of Lindworm, where humans and monsters coexist, a new young doctor, Glenn, begins another day of perilous medical exams! Whether he's examining deep inside a mermaid's gills, stitching up a flesh golem's thigh, assisting a harpy in laying her eggs, or palpating every last scale on a dragon, Glenn is just doing his best to help these girls whose appearances and bodies are all so completely different... so why does he always end up in such precarious positions with his patients? It's all good, though, because it's strictly for medical purposes! He may come close to suffocating from the pressure of his lamia assistant Saphentite's tail coiling around him, but still, the clinic is open for business in this medical fantasy that explores the physiologies of monster girls as never before!

(Source: Crunchyroll)

The first episode premiered a week early on streaming services

node.description:
__[Profile (Lantis)](https://www.lantis.jp/artist/tomas/bio.html)__

__Formed:__ 2015

__Introduction:__
TO-MAS Soundsight Fluorescent Forest, alternatively known as TO-MAS, is a Japanese three-piece music unit under record label Lantis.

__Members:__ 
- [Masumi Itou](https://anilist.co/staff/103635/Masumi-Itou)
- [Youhei Matsui](https://anilist.co/staff/133406/Youhei-Matsui)
- [Mito](https://anilist.co/staff/133408/Mito)

**Height:** 147 cm
**Hobbies:** Singing, drawing, watching anime

[Website](https://suzukiaina.jp/) | [Profile (IAM Agency)](http://iamagency.sukurepo.jp/actors/women/suzuki_aina) | [Twitter](https://twitter.com/aina_suzuki723) | [Agency Twitter](https://twitter.com/AinaSuzuki_Info) | [YouTube](https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCpNypDVlaMyJDx7P8u3dd-A)

She debuted as a voice actress in 2014. She is also skilled in the Minyou (民謡) genre, which is a genre of traditional Japanese music, where she won many competitions.

__Non-anime roles:__
- Sakawa - Azur Lane (VG)

ARCANA PROJECT is a 6-member girl's vocal unit jointly produces by Lantis and DEARSTAGE featuring tarot cards. Mia_REGINA directs songs and dances. 
They made their debut on January 18, 2020, followed by their first organized live "ACE of CUPS" named after minor arcana.

The outfits are based on common design with personalized detail.

Two of them have just joined to DS Gaming Team to appear at eSports contests as well.

They released their pre-debut single ACE of WANDS on March 25, 2020. Due to the COVID-19 outbreak, all release events in March are canceled.

Currently they are performing occasionally at LINELIVE as a whole or part where membership is available instead of appearing at live house due to stayhome situation.

They have proudly announced that they will perform the opening theme for the Monster Girl Doctor Anime which will be airing on 2020 summer. They will release the song as their first single named カンパネラ響く空で(Campanella Hibiku Sora de)

[Wiki (jp)](https://ja.wikipedia.org/wiki/明田川仁)

Affiliated with Magic Capsule, a recording studio led by his father [Susumu Aketagawa](https://anilist.co/staff/120062).
__Kyou Takada__ is a Japanese composer and arranger.

__[Blog (JP)](http://unisen.blog.shinobi.jp/) | [Twitter](https://twitter.com/Yuriko_m)__

__Graduated:__ Ferris University

__Yuriko Mutou__, better known as Yuriko Mori, is a Japanese lyricist.
__Kyou Takada__ is a Japanese composer and arranger.

__[Profile (Heart Company)](https://www.heart-company.co.jp/ando)__ | __[Twitter](https://twitter.com/andosasa)__

__Sasa Andou__ is a Japanese lyricist, who is currently affiliated with the Heart Company. She debuted as a lyricist in the summer of 2017.
